text: Paul Georg Daniel Köhler (31 August 1895 – 17 December 1969) was a Danish diver. He competed in the men's 10 metre springboard event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1895 births Category:1969 deaths Category:Danish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Denmark Category:Divers at the 1920 Summer Olympics
